N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6401.0 - Purpose

State Regulations

The purpose of this Part is to set forth the procedure by
which an applicant may appeal a New York State Council on the Arts decision
denying in whole or in part its program request. Notes
